text.tspan: This document lists the assets, fonts, and colours used for the Indonesian Journal of Biotechnology (IJBiotech).
Contained here are also guidelines on the purposes of each element and how they are to be used. Note that assets
should not be sourced from this document but rather individually from their associated folders.
Main wordmark; to be used when longform journal title is required
Main logo can be used by itself or in conjunction with main wordmark.
Alternative logo should only be used by itself, never with main wordmark.
Author affiliations, abstract content, headers, footers, figure and table captions, website content; article titles,
author names, section headings; subsection headings
